translation[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,52,"Pandema jaŵajinjile kukwakwe ni kuŵecheta kuti: “Ntendele!” Jwalakwe (panyuma pakwajanga ni kwaona kuti ngakulya yakulya yajwaŵichile) jwatite: “Chisimu uwwe tukun’jogopa ŵanganyammwe.”"
  15,53,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Nkajogopa! Chisimu uwwe tukumpa abali jakusengwasya janti chinkole mwanache jwakumanyilila nnope.”"
  15,54,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ana nkundagulila jele abali jakusengwasyaji kutendaga uchekulu uli ungwayiye kala? Ana abali jamboneji nkundagulila m’matalachi?”"
  15,55,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Tukuntagulila abali jamboneji mwakuonaonape; basi ngasim’ba mwa ŵakata tama.”"
  15,56,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ana ninduni jwampaka akate tama kuchanasa cha Ambujegwe, pangaŵaga ŵakupotela?”"
  15,57,"(Kaneka) jwatite: “Abali jao (jine) jaichile nijapi jaomanja akutumidwa?”"
  15,58,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Chisimu uwwe tutumisyidwe ku ŵandu ŵakuleŵa.”"
  15,59,"“Ikaŵeje ŵaliŵasa lya Lutwi, chisimu uwwe chitukajokole ŵanawose.”"
  15,60,"“Pangaŵanga ŵankwao, twapimichisye yanti ŵalakweo chaŵe mwa akusigalila munyuma (chajonanjidwe).”"
  15,61,Basi ndema jaŵaiche akutumidwa kwiŵasa lya Lutwi
  15,62,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Chisimu ŵanganyammwe ni ŵandu ŵangamanyika (kukwangu).”"
  15,63,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Basi tum’bichilile ni ayila (ilagasyo) yaŵaliji nkuikaichila.”"
  15,64,"“Soni tun’jigalile (abali) jakuonaonape, soni chisimu uwwe ŵakuonaonape.”"
  15,65,"“Basi ŵigulani niliŵasa lyenu mu upande wachilo, sano mmwe mwakuyeje munyuma mwao, nambo akasagalauka jwalijose mwa jenumanja (kulola munyuma ndema jakupikana kulindima kwaipotesi yakuuma kwinani, atakwisa mwaawile), ni n’jendelechele (mwakangamala) kuja kunnamulidwe.”"
  15,66,"Ni twammanyisye jwalakwe (Lutwi) lilamusi lyalakweli lyanti: Chisimu njinga sya ŵanganyao (achimakafilio) chisikatidwe (tajonanjidwe) kumasikusiku"
  15,67,Niŵaiche (kwa Lutwi) ŵandu ŵa mu nsinda ali ŵakusengwa (pakupikana kuti ayiche achachanda ŵakusalala kuti ŵatende yausakwa)
  15,68,"(Lutwi) jwatite: “Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa achalendo ŵangu, basi nkandesya soni (pakwatenda yakusakala).”"
  15,69,“Ni mun’jogope Allah soni nkanjigasya nchesela (pameso pao).”
  15,70,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Ana nganitunkanya kupochela ŵandu (ŵachilendo)?”"